text: Olonne-sur-Mer is a former commune. It is found in the region Pays de la Loire in the Vendée department in the west of France. On 1 January 2019, it became a part of the commune of Les Sables-d'Olonne.Arrêté préfectoral 17 August 2018 == References == Category:Former communes in Vendée
title: Olonne-sur-Mer
